<br>
You can't evade while solo.  The mob will just laugh at you.<br>
<br>
I will leave the when-to-evade question to more seasoned stabbers.  Me, I evade every time the mob remembers about me.  At least for me, evade is so unreliable (&quot;You have ducked away from the main combat&quot; WHAM! owwww) that I don't worry much about siccing the thing on the casters.<br>
<br>
Ignore - if I remember correctly, just type /ignore and the person's name again.<br>
<br>
Name - I deleted a character and tried to recreate it immediately, and the name was rejected.  Maybe if you wait awhile, it would work.<br>
<br>
Night vision - I think they have changed this.  My night vision used to be quite good as a half-elf, now it's horrible.  If you have money, you could look for a light source.<br>
<br>
Food - you get your newb food back when you die until level 4 or 5 I think?  At least when I was young, if you banked it, it didn't disappear.  To save on food money, I threw myself off the lift a bunch of times and banked the food.<br>
<br>
Good luck and have fun!<br>
<br>
Pualani Leaozhin<br>
39 Rogue<br>
